OL,3,CForce refers itself to police watchdog
OL,4,Cafter man shot by armed officers
OL,6,FWest Mercia Police has referred itself
OL,7,Fto the Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC), after a man was shot
OL,9,Fby armed police in Worcestershire.
OL,11,FOfficers were called by West Midlands
OL,12,FAmbulance Service to an address on
OL,13,FFownhope Close in Redditch, at around
OL,14,F2pm on Tuesday after concerns were
OL,15,Fraised for the safety of a man with a
OL,16,Fknife.
OL,18,FThe force said attempts were made over
OL,19,F"several hours" to deal with the
OL,20,Fincident, but the man was shot at
OL,21,Faround 7.40pm.
