OL,6,F"We do not underestimate the shock and
OL,7,Fconcern this may cause the local
OL,8,Fcommunity and I want to reassure
OL,9,Fresidents that we are following all
OL,10,Fappropriate procedures, this included
OL,11,Fmaking an immediate referral to the
OL,12,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,13,F(IOPC), as is mandatory and right.
OL,15,FHe adds: "We will support their
OL,16,Finvestigation, which will include
OL,17,Fproviding all information we hold,
OL,18,Fincluding body worn camera footage."
