OL,6,FAn IOPC spokesman said "We can confirm
OL,7,Fwe have begun an independent
OL,8,Finvestigation following an incident at
OL,9,Fan address in Fownhope Close,
OL,10,FRedditch, at around 7.40pm yesterday
OL,11,Fin which a man was shot by police and
OL,12,Fsadly pronounced dead soon after.
OL,14,F"After being informed of the incident
OL,15,Fby West Mercia Police, we sent
OL,16,Finvestigators to the scene ... to
OL,17,Fbegin our inquiries and start
OL,18,Fgathering evidence.
OL,20,F"Our investigation is in its very
OL,21,Fearly stages."
