OL,3,CForce refers itself to police watchdog
OL,4,Cafter man shot by armed officers
OL,6,FThe police watchdog said West Mercia
OL,7,Fofficers had fired Tasers during the
OL,8,Fstand-off with a knife-wielding man,
OL,9,Fbefore a firearms officer shot and
OL,10,Fkilled him.
OL,12,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct said it had seized a knife
OL,14,Ffrom the property, and would be
OL,15,Fexamining police weapons and watching
OL,16,Fbody-word camera footage.
OL,18,FThe officers involved have provided
OL,19,Finitial accounts of what happened.
