OL,11,FThe IOPC director of operations Steve
OL,12,FNoonan said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,13,Fall of those affected by this tragic
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,F"Given a man has died after being shot
OL,17,Fby police, our role is to
OL,18,Findependently investigate all the
OL,19,Fcircumstances surrounding this
OL,20,Fincident including the actions and
OL,21,Fdecisions taken by officers.
