OL,8,Fwill be concerned when it does happen,
OL,9,Fand it is important we conduct a
OL,10,Fdetailed and robust investigation into
OL,11,Fwhat took place".
OL,13,FA tent has been set up at the rear of
OL,14,Fthe building. Tributes have been made
OL,15,Fon social media to the man who died.
OL,17,FOne wrote: "RIP, thoughts are with you
OL,18,Fall."
OL,20,FAnother said: "So sorry to hear this!
OL,21,FSending love to all the family."
